skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: web r. t. c. talks
des:
Listen or watch WebRTC talks and news in your Amazon device.

To start, just say "Alexa, open web r. t. c. talks" or "Alexa, ask web r. t. c. talks to play track one" to start playing the first video.

You can also display videos matching a specific keyword by saying "Alexa, ask web r. t. c. talks to show me videos from 2016".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
